WEBVTT

00:10.491 --> 00:11.631
What's this?

00:11.961 --> 00:13.221
These are kuanxin noodles,

00:13.441 --> 00:15.280
traditionally prepared
by a mother-in-law

00:15.281 --> 00:16.981
for her daughter-in-law

00:17.041 --> 00:18.581
to establish a harmonious relationship.

00:19.121 --> 00:21.461
My mother is no longer alive,

00:24.521 --> 00:25.741
so I'm cooking for you.

00:30.481 --> 00:32.181
Why are there four bowls?

00:42.141 --> 00:43.400
(Memorial Tablet of Song Yichun)

00:43.401 --> 00:44.541
As per tradition,

00:44.861 --> 00:47.061
I should bring my bride
to pray in the ancestral hall,

00:47.721 --> 00:49.261
but my father was a sinner,

00:50.041 --> 00:52.791
(Memorial Tablet of Song Yichun)
so he wasn't admitted into the hall.

00:52.801 --> 00:53.941
These two bowls

00:55.641 --> 00:56.981
are for my parents.

01:01.201 --> 01:03.981
(Memorial Tablet of Song Yichun)

01:08.481 --> 01:09.621
Father.

01:10.521 --> 01:11.661
Mother.

01:12.281 --> 01:13.501
I'm married now.

01:15.241 --> 01:16.501
This is my wife.

01:17.481 --> 01:18.621
We're doing great.

01:20.521 --> 01:24.741
You can rest in peace in heaven.

01:41.341 --> 01:43.421
Why don't you put the tablet
in the ancestral hall?

01:44.601 --> 01:46.901
We'll just pray quietly
without startling anyone.

01:49.521 --> 01:50.640
I'll come with you.

01:50.641 --> 01:53.501
(Memorial Tablet of Song Yichun)

03:12.881 --> 03:17.320
=Blossom=
(Adapted from the novel "Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

03:17.321 --> 03:20.581
=Episode 29=

03:22.041 --> 03:24.111
Ever since the horse market
in Liaodong was founded,

03:24.121 --> 03:26.381
our kingdom signed a treaty
with the Lizhen tribe

03:26.461 --> 03:27.941
and promised not to attack each other.

03:27.971 --> 03:30.680
However, the Lizhen tribesmen have
been invading our borders lately,

03:30.681 --> 03:32.181
stealing our livestock and feed.

03:32.441 --> 03:33.360
Meanwhile, Lord Qing

03:33.361 --> 03:35.221
is using this opportunity
to expand his troops

03:35.321 --> 03:36.901
to raise his own elite soldiers.

03:37.281 --> 03:39.261
His intentions are well known to all.

03:40.121 --> 03:43.101
Today, Lord Qing is known to be good
at recruiting talents,

03:43.361 --> 03:45.021
but in fact, he does so

03:45.161 --> 03:48.461
through promises of status and wealth,
and sometimes threats.

03:49.281 --> 03:50.480
Do you think they'd really

03:50.481 --> 03:52.141
worship him as their master?

03:53.361 --> 03:54.501
They won't.

03:55.541 --> 03:56.911
"Lecture not during chaotic times."

03:56.961 --> 03:58.361
"Abandon not during peaceful times."

03:58.441 --> 03:59.901
"Do help during miserable times."

04:00.261 --> 04:01.981
That's the only way
to gain one's loyalty.

04:03.281 --> 04:04.620
Your Lordship, Your Ladyship.

04:04.621 --> 04:06.000
Official Chen is here.

04:06.001 --> 04:06.860
Show him in.

04:06.861 --> 04:08.001
Yes.

04:12.871 --> 04:14.581
Your Lordship, Your Ladyship.

04:15.121 --> 04:16.921
Our scouts in Liaodong
has sent us some news.

04:19.521 --> 04:20.741
The royal court has determined

04:20.841 --> 04:23.501
that ten shi of horse feed
should be sold for seven taels,

04:23.561 --> 04:25.400
but Lord Qing has been
secretly raising prices

04:25.401 --> 04:29.461
all the way to 20 taels, and has only submitted
30% of the revenue to the palace.

04:29.471 --> 04:31.181
He claimed that it
was the palace's orders.

04:31.341 --> 04:33.240
That's why the Lizhen tribesmen
became furious

04:33.241 --> 04:34.661
and turned rogue,

04:34.881 --> 04:36.341
creating chaos in Liaodong.

04:38.281 --> 04:39.960
Lord Qing is abusing power

04:39.961 --> 04:41.221
for his own wealth.

04:42.361 --> 04:43.440
This is a serious matter.

04:43.441 --> 04:44.721
We need to formulate a solution.

04:45.081 --> 04:46.881
If we act impulsively
without a backup plan,

04:47.201 --> 04:49.320
Lord Qing may learn to cover his tracks

04:49.321 --> 04:50.661
and accuse us instead.

04:54.161 --> 04:57.240
(Meritorious Service)

04:57.241 --> 04:59.520
How dare you secretly worship a sinner?

04:59.521 --> 05:01.381
(Memorial Tablet of Song Yichun)
Give me the tablet!

05:02.561 --> 05:04.381
It's only human
to mourn for one's parents.

05:04.701 --> 05:06.141
I hope you can pardon us this time.

05:06.521 --> 05:09.581
It was the Emperor himself
who declared Song Yichun a sinner.

05:09.641 --> 05:11.400
He's already kind enough
to let this family

05:11.401 --> 05:13.301
retain their dukeship status.

05:13.401 --> 05:14.720
If word of this spreads,

05:14.721 --> 05:17.701
you'd be seen as opposing
the Emperor's orders!

05:17.881 --> 05:19.160
Director Song, Princess.

05:19.161 --> 05:21.021
I'm sure

05:21.681 --> 05:23.781
you'd understand that.

05:26.201 --> 05:27.320
Who are you

05:27.321 --> 05:28.861
to shove my master?

05:31.041 --> 05:32.181
Your master?

05:32.521 --> 05:34.450
That illicit love child

05:34.451 --> 05:36.000
and that dead man

05:36.001 --> 05:37.920
tried to kill the Duchess several times.

05:37.921 --> 05:38.880
How is he a master?

05:38.881 --> 05:40.021
Su Lan, that's enough!

05:42.521 --> 05:43.661
Yes.

05:44.081 --> 05:45.801
You're a princess now.

05:46.041 --> 05:47.531
Of course, you'd protect him.

05:47.841 --> 05:49.461
I can't say no to that.

05:51.401 --> 05:52.541
Su Lan.

05:53.361 --> 05:54.821
Whatever the reason may be,

05:55.151 --> 05:57.641
anyone who offends someone
of a higher rank has to be punished.

05:58.361 --> 05:59.501
Men.

06:00.401 --> 06:01.541
Punish her.

06:09.281 --> 06:10.720
You haughty maid.

06:10.721 --> 06:12.421
You dare to defy the Princess?

06:12.721 --> 06:14.661
Do you have any respect
for the royal family?

06:15.361 --> 06:17.080
If you won't heed the Princess orders,

06:17.081 --> 06:19.981
I'll have to ask
the Empress to interfere

06:20.161 --> 06:22.181
and make sure everyone
in the Duke's residence

06:22.361 --> 06:24.581
know their place.

06:24.921 --> 06:26.000
Men.

06:26.001 --> 06:27.301
Slap her face 20 times.

06:31.001 --> 06:33.981
It was the Prince Consort
who prayed to a sinner.

06:34.121 --> 06:36.381
Please understand this, Princess.

06:40.121 --> 06:41.541
(He just wanted)

06:41.601 --> 06:44.501
(to pray to his parents.)

06:46.801 --> 06:48.461
Why are you still standing there?

06:48.841 --> 06:50.421
Didn't you hear what I said?

06:51.241 --> 06:52.461
Slap her face 20 times!

07:11.601 --> 07:12.741
Stop that!

07:13.841 --> 07:15.021
- Get up.
- Out of the way!

07:17.841 --> 07:19.120
Your Ladyship.

07:19.121 --> 07:21.021
- Your maid has been very brazen.
- Are you fine?

07:21.321 --> 07:23.021
First, she insulted Second Young Master,

07:23.121 --> 07:24.781
then rebutted the Princess.

07:25.521 --> 07:27.360
Are all your servants

07:27.361 --> 07:29.600
so disrespectful?

07:29.601 --> 07:30.841
What do you know about respect?

07:31.161 --> 07:32.701
Is this how you talk to me?

07:33.241 --> 07:34.880
Zhao, I punished her because...

07:34.881 --> 07:36.000
Sister-in-law.

07:36.001 --> 07:37.181
It's not the Princess's fault.

07:37.401 --> 07:38.541
Su Lan...

07:39.281 --> 07:40.661
She kept calling me an illicit...

07:44.761 --> 07:45.901
Forget it.

07:46.081 --> 07:47.341
This row started because of me.

07:47.521 --> 07:48.541
Don't blame her.

07:48.551 --> 07:50.381
I know you've been gossiping
behind our backs.

07:50.401 --> 07:52.840
But they are still newly married.

07:52.841 --> 07:54.461
What will the Princess think?

08:06.401 --> 08:08.320
I just warned you,

08:08.321 --> 08:09.601
and you still dare to talk back?

08:12.081 --> 08:13.661
Sister-in-law, if you think I'm wrong,

08:14.321 --> 08:15.621
then I'm wrong.

08:16.041 --> 08:18.031
Please don't put the Princess
in a difficult position

08:18.161 --> 08:19.421
and hurt your friendship.

08:34.521 --> 08:36.221
It was my idea
to pray to his father here.

08:37.681 --> 08:39.181
If the Emperor has to punish someone,

08:40.081 --> 08:41.821
I'll take the full blame.

08:42.961 --> 08:44.101
However, Su Lan

08:45.001 --> 08:47.021
has insulted the Prince Consort

08:47.241 --> 08:48.981
several times in public.

08:51.441 --> 08:53.821
I hope you can give me an explanation.

08:55.321 --> 08:56.461
Miao Ansu!

08:56.521 --> 08:59.421
Have you forgotten our friendship
just because you got married?

08:59.481 --> 09:00.520
Exactly!

09:00.521 --> 09:02.040
Even a dog is better than you!

09:02.041 --> 09:03.181
Su Lan!

09:07.521 --> 09:08.661
Well said.

09:10.401 --> 09:12.221
At least Su Lan has exposed

09:13.681 --> 09:15.781
the truth behind
our so-called friendship.

09:17.161 --> 09:18.301
Zhao.

09:19.121 --> 09:20.701
What do you take me for?

09:23.041 --> 09:24.661
How could you ask me that?

09:25.121 --> 09:26.661
Now, I don't know

09:28.121 --> 09:30.341
whether you're good to me

09:31.401 --> 09:32.821
because you saw me as a friend,

09:33.921 --> 09:35.821
or because you pitied me.

09:37.801 --> 09:39.341
If we're truly friends,

09:39.881 --> 09:42.101
now that my husband and I are insulted,

09:42.801 --> 09:44.781
can't I even defend ourselves?

09:56.881 --> 09:58.021
Had I not come,

09:58.121 --> 10:00.141
you would've killed Dou Zhao here,
wouldn't you?

10:03.161 --> 10:04.821
What happened to her?

10:06.681 --> 10:07.981
Summon Official Lu now.

10:30.321 --> 10:32.381
Zhao must have been too angry.

10:33.061 --> 10:35.731
It's impossible to reinstate your
father's tablet in the hall now.

10:36.101 --> 10:37.241
I heard that Sister-in-law

10:37.801 --> 10:39.421
has been working too hard,

10:40.171 --> 10:42.461
so she probably passed out
from exhaustion.

10:42.991 --> 10:44.131
Don't overthink it.

10:46.571 --> 10:48.941
It's just that it's obvious

10:50.681 --> 10:53.101
that a maid is closer to her
than you are.

10:54.281 --> 10:57.301
It was Su Lan who insulted us first,

10:57.521 --> 10:59.341
yet she only blamed you
for punishing her.

10:59.791 --> 11:01.661
She misunderstood you before.

11:04.041 --> 11:06.101
Has my relationship with her turned sour

11:07.001 --> 11:08.781
since we got married?

11:09.321 --> 11:10.741
But why?

11:11.281 --> 11:12.941
Some things change for the worse,

11:13.841 --> 11:15.960
but some change for the better.

11:15.961 --> 11:18.760
(Melody of Bamboo and Pines)

11:18.761 --> 11:20.981
Perhaps it's normal for one
to give up on certain things

11:22.121 --> 11:23.781
when they find the love of their life.

11:27.681 --> 11:28.821
It's my fault.

11:29.161 --> 11:30.301
I'm sorry.

11:52.121 --> 11:53.261
Well?

11:53.361 --> 11:55.141
Her kidneys are acting up

11:55.401 --> 11:58.000
because of exhaustion,

11:58.001 --> 11:59.941
and her uterus is rather cold,

12:00.561 --> 12:02.541
which makes pregnancy hard.

12:10.241 --> 12:11.381
What should we do?

12:11.841 --> 12:13.021
So,

12:14.681 --> 12:16.901
you are very lucky that Her Ladyship

12:17.561 --> 12:20.621
could get pregnant this time.

12:22.401 --> 12:24.501
She's pregnant?

12:24.801 --> 12:25.941
Yes.

12:30.521 --> 12:31.480
Ms. Longevity.

12:31.481 --> 12:32.621
We have a child now.

12:34.961 --> 12:37.621
Is the child healthy?

12:37.961 --> 12:39.181
Your child is fine,

12:39.281 --> 12:41.101
but your body is weak,

12:41.241 --> 12:43.581
and the first three months
are the riskiest.

12:43.681 --> 12:46.261
You have to be much more careful.

12:49.401 --> 12:50.560
Thank you, Official Lu.

12:50.561 --> 12:51.781
Thank you, Official Lu.

12:51.881 --> 12:53.941
I take my leave.

12:54.121 --> 12:55.581
Su Lan, walk him out.

13:10.001 --> 13:11.141
But...

13:11.681 --> 13:12.821
Ms. Longevity.

13:13.241 --> 13:14.421
Giving birth is risky,

13:14.961 --> 13:16.301
and I'm meant to die soon.

13:17.121 --> 13:19.160
Just tell me if you
don't want this child.

13:19.161 --> 13:20.301
I want it.

13:24.681 --> 13:27.821
I want my child to be born

13:28.361 --> 13:30.181
healthily and safely.

13:31.521 --> 13:33.101
I've even thought of names.

13:33.381 --> 13:36.341
If it's a boy, we'll name him Zhiyi.

13:36.561 --> 13:39.101
If it's a girl, then she'll be Lianjun.

13:39.761 --> 13:41.021
"You know my mind

13:41.401 --> 13:42.741
and feel my compassion.

13:42.881 --> 13:44.501
It is a love that needs no questions.

13:44.681 --> 13:46.021
As paddy turns to rice

13:46.201 --> 13:47.461
and candle becomes tears,

13:47.841 --> 13:49.581
our love will bloom."

13:50.561 --> 13:51.701
Those are nice names.

13:53.721 --> 13:57.261
(Iridescent Colors)

13:59.041 --> 14:01.141
(Memorial Tablet of Song Yichun)

14:02.481 --> 14:03.621
Second Young Master.

14:03.801 --> 14:06.501
I thought you wanted to pray
to the late Duke this morning?

14:07.121 --> 14:08.640
Why are you...

14:08.641 --> 14:09.781
Did you really think

14:10.441 --> 14:12.781
I wanted to pray to my useless father?

14:15.161 --> 14:17.341
He has no right to enter
the ancestral hall.

14:19.481 --> 14:23.021
(Memorial Tablet of Song Yichun)

14:25.161 --> 14:28.461
(Passing Days)

14:30.561 --> 14:32.160
Today will be the last time Ji Yong

14:32.161 --> 14:33.501
performs acupuncture on Qi Xia.

14:34.561 --> 14:36.101
It's been quite a while.

14:36.481 --> 14:38.901
I wonder how Qi Xia is doing now.

14:39.361 --> 14:40.760
Madam, you should be resting

14:40.761 --> 14:42.381
instead of coming out.

14:42.841 --> 14:44.221
Lord Buddha.

14:44.321 --> 14:47.501
I, Miao Ansu, will worship you
for the rest of my life.

14:47.881 --> 14:49.360
May I receive your blessings.

14:49.361 --> 14:52.981
First, I hope my family can enjoy
peace and longevity.

14:53.321 --> 14:55.160
Second, I hope
that my dear friend Dou Zhao

14:55.161 --> 14:58.461
will be free from calamity
and lead a good life.

14:58.961 --> 15:00.760
Third, I hope that Dou Zhao and I

15:00.761 --> 15:04.101
can resolve our differences
and reconcile.

15:17.401 --> 15:18.541
Zhao.

15:20.441 --> 15:21.600
You can leave first.

15:21.601 --> 15:23.400
I'd like to talk to Zhao alone.

15:23.401 --> 15:24.741
Yes, Princess.

15:30.601 --> 15:33.261
I heard that praying to the Buddha
in Wanfo Temple does work.

15:35.241 --> 15:38.141
I guess my third wish has been granted.

15:39.241 --> 15:40.901
Zhao, you're not angry at me anymore?

15:43.121 --> 15:45.021
No matter how much misunderstanding
we may have,

15:45.241 --> 15:47.061
you're still my best friend.

15:47.221 --> 15:48.741
I wouldn't hold a grudge against you.

15:55.041 --> 15:56.181
Ansu.

15:57.081 --> 15:58.621
Whether it's our friends or husbands,

15:59.361 --> 16:01.741
we chose them to become
part of our family.

16:02.841 --> 16:04.621
I hope you won't regret.

16:06.321 --> 16:08.101
I know you care for me,

16:08.361 --> 16:10.181
but Song Han is not a bad person.

16:10.321 --> 16:12.600
As the youngest son of a duke,

16:12.601 --> 16:14.460
he had never experienced suffering.

16:14.461 --> 16:16.341
Now that his parents have passed away,

16:16.521 --> 16:17.480
he got too overwhelmed.

16:17.481 --> 16:19.061
That's why he's changed drastically.

16:20.401 --> 16:22.981
I guess there are some things
that you should know.

16:23.121 --> 16:24.261
Ansu!

16:30.881 --> 16:32.131
Your body is weak.

16:32.241 --> 16:34.141
It's windy and smoky here.

16:34.161 --> 16:35.341
You might collapse.

16:36.121 --> 16:38.541
Since Sister-in-law stays nearby,

16:38.801 --> 16:41.221
you can save your conversation
for next time.

16:43.441 --> 16:44.581
Zhao.

16:44.601 --> 16:46.821
I'm going home now.
Let's catch up sometime.

16:47.681 --> 16:49.261
- Sure.
- Men.

16:49.481 --> 16:50.741
Escort the Princess back home.

16:53.951 --> 16:55.091
This way, Princess.

17:02.121 --> 17:04.981
I know your tricks.

17:05.561 --> 17:06.861
I've been tolerating you

17:07.481 --> 17:09.901
because Ansu had a turbulent past,

17:10.601 --> 17:12.181
and she truly loves you,

17:12.421 --> 17:14.541
so I didn't want to ruin the man
she's relying on.

17:15.401 --> 17:18.101
However, I now see

17:19.201 --> 17:21.381
that you're taking advantage
of Ansu's love

17:21.391 --> 17:23.840
and the last shred of brotherhood
you share with your brother

17:23.841 --> 17:25.501
to commit unlawful things.

17:25.881 --> 17:27.501
If you don't stop soon,

17:27.721 --> 17:29.541
you will face the consequences,

17:29.801 --> 17:31.541
and I won't let you off.

17:34.481 --> 17:36.301
Sister-in-law, you're still acting

17:36.641 --> 17:38.741
like you're holier than all of us.

17:39.001 --> 17:40.341
Who do you think you are?

17:40.681 --> 17:41.861
A judge?

17:42.521 --> 17:43.661
A king?

17:44.161 --> 17:45.421
Or a god?

17:46.061 --> 17:48.261
I'm just fighting
for what should be mine.

17:48.361 --> 17:49.541
How is that wrong?

17:50.071 --> 17:51.391
In fact, Sister-in-law,

17:51.611 --> 17:52.981
you've been meddling too much.

17:53.551 --> 17:55.901
One day, you'll bear
the brunt of your actions,

17:55.961 --> 17:58.581
and you might hurt yourself.

18:01.721 --> 18:02.891
I take my leave.

18:07.921 --> 18:09.611
How stubborn.

18:10.201 --> 18:12.840
I thought Miss Miao had changed
after she became a princess,

18:12.841 --> 18:15.371
but she still had the heart
to pray for Madam.

18:15.601 --> 18:16.990
I guess childhood friendships

18:16.991 --> 18:18.341
don't change easily.

18:18.361 --> 18:19.501
Your Ladyship!

18:21.121 --> 18:22.261
Your Ladyship.

18:22.561 --> 18:23.970
My wife has recovered.

18:23.971 --> 18:25.321
Qi Xia has recovered!

18:25.951 --> 18:27.091
Bring me to her now.

18:34.521 --> 18:36.221
She's recovered from epilepsy,

18:36.311 --> 18:37.700
but her nerves have been damaged,

18:37.701 --> 18:39.910
so her cognition
is not fully restored yet.

18:39.911 --> 18:41.421
She needs more rest,

18:41.641 --> 18:43.341
so don't exhaust her.

18:47.881 --> 18:49.021
Qi Xia.

18:49.361 --> 18:50.541
Do you recognize me?

18:51.721 --> 18:53.261
Of course I do.

18:53.361 --> 18:54.781
You're my husband.

18:55.721 --> 18:58.061
This is wonderful.

18:59.081 --> 19:00.080
Thank you, Your Ladyship!

19:00.081 --> 19:01.240
Thank you, Master Ji!

19:01.241 --> 19:03.181
Since Qi Xia has recovered,

19:03.361 --> 19:05.720
why don't you work in Yizhi Hall

19:05.721 --> 19:07.141
to take care of her?

19:09.841 --> 19:10.720
Come on, Qi Xia.

19:10.721 --> 19:12.781
Come on, let's kowtow to Her Ladyship!

19:13.641 --> 19:14.901
Please get up.

19:15.161 --> 19:16.100
Su Xin, Su Lan.

19:16.101 --> 19:17.080
Take them back.

19:17.081 --> 19:18.421
- Yes, Your Ladyship.
- Yes, Your Ladyship.

19:18.641 --> 19:19.781
Come on.

19:27.521 --> 19:29.461
Thank you for your help again.

19:30.001 --> 19:31.661
She was destined to recover.

19:34.161 --> 19:35.920
If you're not in a rush,

19:35.921 --> 19:37.381
stay with me a while more.

19:38.041 --> 19:39.181
What is it?

19:40.041 --> 19:42.521
I'd like to teach you
the 13 Acupuncture Spots of the Demons.

19:43.241 --> 19:44.821
The 13 Acupuncture Spots of the Demons?

19:46.441 --> 19:48.861
There's a meridian spot
under the tongue.

19:49.041 --> 19:51.751
When you perform acupuncture there,
we call it "sealing the demon".

19:51.761 --> 19:54.101
It's a very unusual method
that is hard to master.

19:54.401 --> 19:57.000
However, it works miracles on patients
who are in a coma

19:57.001 --> 19:58.901
or in critical condition.

20:02.481 --> 20:04.581
They say physicians shine
during troubled times.

20:05.181 --> 20:08.031
I wish the world is free of illness,
and that physicians are not needed.

20:09.281 --> 20:10.541
Other than acupuncture,

20:11.121 --> 20:13.261
is there anything else
you want to tell me?

20:21.441 --> 20:23.741
You've been my medical student,

20:24.241 --> 20:26.061
and this is probably your last lesson.

20:30.001 --> 20:32.061
Injuries are common
among Lord Qing's troops.

20:33.681 --> 20:35.501
Even ten physicians
cannot compare to you.

20:35.881 --> 20:37.061
For that,

20:37.401 --> 20:38.621
if I were Lord Qing,

20:39.001 --> 20:41.541
I'd do all I can to make you
stay in Liaodong.

20:41.601 --> 20:43.981
Moreover, you're also
a brilliant strategist.

20:47.041 --> 20:48.381
You flatter me.

20:49.401 --> 20:51.301
You didn't come back
to the capital to rest.

20:51.651 --> 20:53.360
It was Lord Qing
who ordered you to return

20:53.361 --> 20:54.621
to do something else.

20:55.841 --> 20:57.701
And you approached me right away

20:57.961 --> 20:59.781
because it's part
of Lord Qing's plan, right?

21:00.661 --> 21:02.181
I don't want to hide anything from you,

21:02.921 --> 21:04.341
and I know I can't.

21:05.641 --> 21:06.781
Forget it.

21:07.881 --> 21:09.901
Before we proceed to the boring talk,

21:10.641 --> 21:12.381
come with me.

21:29.281 --> 21:30.421
Little Zhuang Zhou.

21:31.881 --> 21:33.181
Do you remember this place?

21:34.361 --> 21:35.501
Of course.

21:36.161 --> 21:38.061
The cracks on the mirror
are still there.

21:38.631 --> 21:39.771
You're finally awake.

21:39.991 --> 21:41.440
Have you gone crazy from reading?

21:41.441 --> 21:43.261
You knocked your head on the mirror.

21:45.641 --> 21:47.861
I still remember the alignment
of the stars that day.

21:48.281 --> 21:49.901
There is hope hidden in the darkness,

21:50.601 --> 21:51.941
and they're bound by karma.

21:52.281 --> 21:54.421
I thought I was your karma,

21:56.281 --> 21:57.701
but I was wrong.

21:58.521 --> 22:00.101
The final result was a turbulent world.

22:02.041 --> 22:03.381
I didn't expect

22:03.721 --> 22:05.381
that my most trusted friend

22:06.441 --> 22:08.141
would become the cause of it.

22:09.641 --> 22:11.621
Is this what your ambition is?

22:12.521 --> 22:15.341
What I want is to lead the cabinet
and restore the kingdom's glory.

22:16.801 --> 22:19.581
I want the person who trusts me
the most to become the Emperor.

22:19.601 --> 22:22.401
Even if war breaks out in Liaodong,
causing pain and suffering?

22:22.421 --> 22:23.680
As long as Lord Qing
follows my instructions,

22:23.681 --> 22:25.000
he won't have to resort to violence.

22:25.001 --> 22:27.000
Is this why you chose
to serve a traitor?

22:27.001 --> 22:28.760
Since ancient times, the only way

22:28.761 --> 22:30.760
to determine a traitor or pioneer

22:30.761 --> 22:32.141
depends on whether they win.

22:32.641 --> 22:35.981
So, when you were helping
the Miao family back in Futing,

22:36.241 --> 22:38.021
you've already planned this?

22:38.121 --> 22:40.501
Getting close to Lord Qing
through Mu Chuan

22:40.881 --> 22:42.181
was just the first step.

22:42.361 --> 22:43.821
When the bandits invaded the capital,

22:44.721 --> 22:47.461
the Crown Prince lost
almost all of his troops.

22:49.521 --> 22:50.701
Were you part of it too?

22:53.041 --> 22:55.821
Years ago, when Song Yichun released
Li Yaoniang from the Music Office,

22:56.041 --> 22:57.881
he had to go through
the Ministry of Justice.

22:57.881 --> 22:59.021
Since then,

22:59.961 --> 23:01.520
he was already secretly

23:01.521 --> 23:02.760
affiliated to Lord Qing.

23:02.761 --> 23:04.021
I'm asking about you.

23:04.161 --> 23:05.301
Yes.

23:05.501 --> 23:07.931
It was my idea to suppress Song Mo
by manipulating Song Yichun

23:07.941 --> 23:09.181
and the Dou family.

23:09.201 --> 23:11.671
He was the root cause of the issue,
and that was the only solution.

23:11.681 --> 23:14.040
Like playing a game of chess,
I have to play by my strategies.

23:14.041 --> 23:17.221
If the bandits killed me that night,

23:17.721 --> 23:19.611
would you still act so nonchalant?

23:20.201 --> 23:22.061
So, everyone else are just your pawns,

23:22.321 --> 23:23.920
and they must belong to either side?

23:23.921 --> 23:25.870
But, I won't let you die.

23:25.871 --> 23:28.301
I won't let you risk your life
for those pawns.

23:28.761 --> 23:29.901
Yes.

23:30.601 --> 23:32.541
I planned everything all along.

23:33.041 --> 23:34.040
But, I've also given you

23:34.041 --> 23:35.920
countless chances to escape.

23:35.921 --> 23:38.080
Had you chosen to leave with me,

23:38.081 --> 23:40.080
I would've given everything up
and start again!

23:40.081 --> 23:41.221
But you?

23:43.281 --> 23:44.781
How could you be so stupid

23:45.681 --> 23:47.461
to fall in love with Song Mo?

23:55.321 --> 23:56.461
Dou Zhao.

23:58.481 --> 24:00.461
My scheme is nowhere near completion.

24:01.321 --> 24:04.301
If you want to keep yourself
and Song Mo safe,

24:06.041 --> 24:08.501
tell him to resign his position
in the Imperial Guards.

24:09.281 --> 24:11.261
I'll make sure
that the both of you stay safe.

24:12.601 --> 24:14.381
The snow ganoderma lucidum does exist.

24:15.121 --> 24:16.501
I didn't lie to you.

24:16.801 --> 24:17.941
Ji Jianming.

24:20.841 --> 24:22.781
Disappointment
is the worst feeling of all.

24:24.201 --> 24:26.621
You were my most trusted friend.

24:28.001 --> 24:29.661
But I know very well

24:31.121 --> 24:33.000
that you'd never turn back.

24:33.001 --> 24:34.941
Why should I turn back?

24:35.041 --> 24:36.540
This is the quickest way.

24:36.541 --> 24:37.400
In just two years,

24:37.401 --> 24:39.741
the kingdom will rise from the ashes.

24:39.761 --> 24:41.101
Then, tell me.

24:41.841 --> 24:45.621
Other than Dou Shishu,
Song Yichun, and Mu Chuan,

24:46.241 --> 24:48.421
who else besides me
is working for Lord Qing?

24:52.001 --> 24:53.541
You shouldn't ask things

24:54.481 --> 24:55.981
that I'm not supposed to say.

25:14.681 --> 25:18.341
Our friendship ends today.

25:18.601 --> 25:19.941
The next time we meet,

25:20.601 --> 25:22.181
we will be enemies.

25:23.841 --> 25:25.360
Must you side with the Crown Prince?

25:25.361 --> 25:26.901
This has nothing to do with you.

25:49.001 --> 25:50.461
I knew you'd come.

25:52.041 --> 25:53.181
Of course.

25:53.881 --> 25:55.661
You've laid out an ambush here.

25:56.521 --> 25:58.341
You wanted to kill us, right?

25:59.441 --> 26:00.581
Halt!

26:07.041 --> 26:08.381
Let them go.

26:12.761 --> 26:13.901
Song Mo.

26:16.241 --> 26:17.120
One day, you will

26:17.121 --> 26:18.781
understand my intentions today.

26:20.161 --> 26:21.501
But, no matter what,

26:22.321 --> 26:24.461
before you die,

26:24.641 --> 26:26.381
please leave Dou Zhao

26:27.081 --> 26:28.581
and don't get her involved.

26:54.561 --> 26:55.701
Cuizhu.

26:58.321 --> 27:00.440
Are there any maids serving
the Prince Consort now?

27:00.441 --> 27:01.680
The Prince Consort said

27:01.681 --> 27:02.920
he doesn't wish to be bothered

27:02.921 --> 27:04.581
when he's resting.

27:33.881 --> 27:35.821
Get me a thick blanket.

27:35.841 --> 27:36.981
Yes, Your Highness.

28:22.961 --> 28:25.541
Didn't I tell you not to get near me
when I'm sleeping?

28:26.841 --> 28:28.381
I didn't want you to catch a cold,

28:28.441 --> 28:29.941
so I got you a blanket.

28:30.801 --> 28:32.861
Sorry, I...

28:36.721 --> 28:38.301
I'm sorry.

28:39.841 --> 28:40.981
Someone!

28:42.281 --> 28:43.200
Summon a physician.

28:43.201 --> 28:44.741
- Right away.
- Wait.

28:50.681 --> 28:52.141
I'm fine, Muyu.

28:53.051 --> 28:54.240
No need to summon a physician.

28:54.241 --> 28:55.381
You may leave now.

28:55.681 --> 28:57.021
- Yes, Your Highness.
- Yes, Your Highness.

29:00.081 --> 29:01.221
I...

29:02.641 --> 29:04.021
I didn't mean to do that.

29:05.241 --> 29:06.901
Let me go outside to calm down.

29:08.001 --> 29:09.141
Muyu.

29:12.441 --> 29:13.741
Don't be nervous.

29:14.561 --> 29:16.261
I'm really fine.

29:17.921 --> 29:19.061
Come with me.

29:20.521 --> 29:21.661
Come on.

29:28.561 --> 29:29.701
Here.

29:31.321 --> 29:32.821
Ansu, I...

29:33.561 --> 29:34.701
Sit down.

29:41.121 --> 29:42.261
Lie down.

29:43.321 --> 29:44.501
No, Ansu.

29:44.761 --> 29:45.981
I might hurt you again.

29:48.001 --> 29:49.821
You won't hurt me again.

30:01.041 --> 30:02.661
Lie down.

30:04.481 --> 30:06.821
You have to lie down to sleep.

30:07.121 --> 30:08.261
Listen to me.

30:11.681 --> 30:13.581
Put your legs up and sleep.

30:25.641 --> 30:27.701
Everything will get better.

30:28.441 --> 30:29.581
It'll be fine.

31:04.441 --> 31:05.581
Mother.

31:11.281 --> 31:12.421
Mother.

31:36.681 --> 31:39.131
♪I rise on tiptoes♪

31:39.481 --> 31:41.570
♪To kiss your brow♪

31:41.571 --> 31:46.891
♪From now on,
my heart needs no disguise♪

31:47.381 --> 31:49.831
♪Wrapped in frost and snow♪

31:50.221 --> 31:52.240
♪Standing side by side with you♪

31:52.241 --> 31:56.981
♪Looking at this kaleidoscopic world♪

31:57.361 --> 32:02.641
♪I hold onto this love
for the world to see♪

32:03.121 --> 32:07.231
♪Accumulated in this life,
now fulfilled♪

32:08.161 --> 32:13.951
♪Not heeding the people's advice♪

32:14.421 --> 32:20.761
♪Our love is as clear as the moon,
no false words in sight♪

32:21.491 --> 32:26.880
♪I close our distance without rest♪

32:26.881 --> 32:32.220
♪I devote my life and
world to your wishes♪

32:32.221 --> 32:35.261
♪Not afraid of our encounter♪

32:35.481 --> 32:37.800
♪Time bends and breaks♪

32:37.801 --> 32:42.840
♪Thankfully, I can make it up to you
for the rest of my life♪

32:42.841 --> 32:48.230
♪I pluck the stars and the moon
to illuminate your night♪

32:48.231 --> 32:53.760
♪My heart has room only for one,
filled to the brim♪

32:53.761 --> 32:56.531
♪Fully aware of the fleeting moments
in the world♪

32:56.881 --> 32:59.150
♪Most love problems are hard to resolve♪

32:59.151 --> 33:04.061
♪For you, I rise again in this life♪

33:04.171 --> 33:09.181
♪I close our distance without rest♪

33:09.531 --> 33:14.441
♪I devote my life and world
to your wishes♪

33:14.841 --> 33:17.821
♪Not afraid of our encounter♪

33:18.241 --> 33:20.470
♪Time bends and breaks♪

33:20.471 --> 33:25.610
♪Thankfully, I can make it up to you
for the rest of my life♪

33:25.611 --> 33:30.830
♪I pluck the stars and the moon
to illuminate your night♪

33:30.831 --> 33:36.250
♪My heart has room only for one,
filled to the brim♪

33:36.251 --> 33:41.900
♪Fully aware of the fleeting moments
in the world♪

33:41.901 --> 33:46.461
♪For you, I rise again in this life♪

33:46.881 --> 33:50.561
♪Without regret♪

34:03.241 --> 34:04.240
Sister.

34:04.241 --> 34:05.680
I just want 3,000 taels.

34:05.681 --> 34:06.960
It's urgent.

34:06.961 --> 34:08.221
That's a lot of money.

34:08.641 --> 34:10.261
Why do you need it?

34:11.281 --> 34:12.160
What else?

34:12.161 --> 34:13.541
I lost my money in business.

34:13.921 --> 34:15.960
I told you that business seemed fishy.

34:15.961 --> 34:17.040
And your friends

34:17.041 --> 34:18.360
doesn't look like decent people.

34:18.361 --> 34:19.280
"I told you."

34:19.281 --> 34:20.501
What is there to tell me now?

34:20.521 --> 34:21.600
Just give me the money.

34:21.601 --> 34:22.600
Anping.

34:22.601 --> 34:24.040
You've been spending

34:24.041 --> 34:25.460
more than you can afford.

34:25.461 --> 34:26.320
What do you mean?

34:26.321 --> 34:27.680
I haven't been spending much.

34:27.681 --> 34:29.301
That's enough. Stop fighting.

34:30.281 --> 34:31.421
Ansu.

34:31.841 --> 34:33.101
Listen.

34:33.801 --> 34:35.661
Even though you're the elder sister,

34:35.881 --> 34:37.781
but you're still a woman.

34:37.841 --> 34:38.720
You've been managing

34:38.721 --> 34:40.181
the family's business well,

34:40.641 --> 34:41.600
but you have to know

34:41.601 --> 34:43.280
that everything belongs to your brother.

34:43.281 --> 34:44.320
Exactly.

34:44.321 --> 34:46.261
Don't interfere in this.

34:46.961 --> 34:48.341
All your money is mine.

34:48.361 --> 34:50.301
I'm just letting you keep it for me.

34:50.321 --> 34:52.361
You won't even give me
a few thousand taels now.

34:52.521 --> 34:53.981
Just this month alone,

34:54.161 --> 34:55.360
Anping has spent 1,000 taels

34:55.361 --> 34:56.560
on drinking

34:56.561 --> 34:57.861
and clothing.

34:58.041 --> 34:59.600
Money doesn't fall from the sky.

34:59.601 --> 35:01.701
We can't afford to spend it
like it's unlimited.

35:02.081 --> 35:03.221
As for your business venture,

35:03.681 --> 35:05.381
we need to look into it and plan.

35:06.401 --> 35:07.520
What now?

35:07.521 --> 35:08.680
Now that you're a princess,

35:08.681 --> 35:10.981
your brother can't use
your money anymore?

35:11.041 --> 35:13.440
Why did I give birth
to such a bad daughter?

35:13.441 --> 35:14.581
I...

35:15.161 --> 35:16.360
- Mother!
- My wife!

35:16.361 --> 35:17.800
- Mother!
- Go away!

35:17.801 --> 35:19.621
I'm so mad now.

35:20.181 --> 35:21.480
Look how you've angered Mother.

35:21.481 --> 35:22.741
Are you still my sister?

35:23.121 --> 35:25.280
You must be a traitor.

35:25.281 --> 35:26.680
You must be using our family's money

35:26.681 --> 35:28.621
to repay your husband's debts!

35:28.841 --> 35:31.021
- I'm fine.
- Mother, everything's fine.

35:31.401 --> 35:32.250
Don't be mad.

35:32.251 --> 35:35.520
- Why do I have a daughter like her?
- I'm here, don't be mad.

35:35.521 --> 35:36.640
- I'm so...
- Hush now.

35:36.641 --> 35:38.661
Entertain our guests, girls.

35:39.361 --> 35:41.261
You're here, sir.

35:41.361 --> 35:42.480
Here, this way.

35:42.481 --> 35:43.680
Come on.

35:43.681 --> 35:45.381
Fill my cup.

35:47.801 --> 35:48.941
Anping.

35:49.961 --> 35:51.860
You are the Princess's only brother

35:51.861 --> 35:53.661
and the only son of your family.

35:54.121 --> 35:55.661
It's only natural

35:55.881 --> 35:57.871
that you should manage

35:58.081 --> 35:59.941
all of your family's assets.

36:00.841 --> 36:02.581
Of course.

36:03.361 --> 36:05.981
You sure know how to talk.

36:08.081 --> 36:09.741
Thanks to my sister,

36:09.921 --> 36:12.701
you're now rich and promoted.

36:13.161 --> 36:14.821
When you succeed in the future,

36:15.001 --> 36:16.821
don't forget our family.

36:19.481 --> 36:20.720
I will always remember

36:20.721 --> 36:23.501
what the Princess has done for me.

36:24.401 --> 36:25.640
Since you're here, Anping,

36:25.641 --> 36:27.061
you should just

36:27.161 --> 36:28.661
enjoy yourself.

36:42.211 --> 36:43.981
Greetings, Lord Song. My name is Zishu.

36:50.281 --> 36:51.421
Zishu.

36:52.361 --> 36:54.821
Come here and greet Mr. Miao.

36:58.361 --> 37:00.181
Greetings, Mr. Miao.

37:02.311 --> 37:06.421
I didn't expect such a beauty
to work here.

37:14.611 --> 37:16.601
Allow me to fill your cup.

37:17.791 --> 37:19.161
Fill my cup!

37:24.521 --> 37:26.781
I'm Princess Anyu's only brother.

37:28.351 --> 37:30.960
Are you all happy, good sirs?

37:30.961 --> 37:32.661
Come on, dance!

37:33.601 --> 37:35.381
Greetings, Lord Song.

37:36.081 --> 37:37.680
Greetings, Mr. Miao.

37:37.681 --> 37:39.661
This morning,

37:39.681 --> 37:40.840
someone has already

37:40.841 --> 37:43.861
requested Zishu to serve them today.

37:44.121 --> 37:45.381
According to the rules,

37:45.521 --> 37:47.600
I have to bring Zishu to...

37:47.601 --> 37:48.741
Who?

37:48.881 --> 37:50.320
Who's so bold

37:50.321 --> 37:51.600
to steal my woman?

37:51.601 --> 37:52.920
- Dear sir.
- Zishu!

37:52.921 --> 37:54.000
No, Mr. Miao!

37:54.001 --> 37:55.341
Where's Zishu?

37:55.481 --> 37:56.621
Mr. Miao!

37:56.681 --> 37:58.101
- Mr. Miao!
- Mr. Miao!

37:58.251 --> 37:59.160
Calm down, Mr. Miao!

37:59.161 --> 38:00.981
- Mr. Miao!
- Mr. Miao!

38:01.121 --> 38:02.000
Mr. Miao!

38:02.001 --> 38:03.981
Mr. Miao, listen to me!

38:04.881 --> 38:06.400
- Zishu!
- Excuse me, sir.

38:06.401 --> 38:07.900
- Zishu!
- Calm down!

38:07.901 --> 38:09.391
- Where's Zishu?
- Mr. Miao!

38:09.401 --> 38:10.821
Who's trying to steal Zishu from me?

38:10.831 --> 38:12.341
- I think it's them.
- Zishu.

38:15.361 --> 38:16.320
Buzz off.

38:16.321 --> 38:18.000
- Out of my way.
- You're not needed here.

38:18.001 --> 38:20.421
So, you're the one who's trying
to steal Zishu from me?

38:21.681 --> 38:22.821
Yeah.

38:26.601 --> 38:27.741
Who are you?

38:28.121 --> 38:29.421
Listen,

38:29.441 --> 38:30.781
I'm the...

38:30.881 --> 38:32.181
Who cares?

38:32.961 --> 38:34.200
Mr. Miao!

38:34.201 --> 38:35.861
Don't fight, please!

38:36.281 --> 38:37.621
We can talk it out!

38:40.121 --> 38:41.480
He missed!

38:41.481 --> 38:42.861
Punch me here.

38:44.321 --> 38:46.221
Damn you!

38:49.401 --> 38:51.421
Mr. Miao!

39:11.961 --> 39:13.101
Your Highness!

39:13.281 --> 39:14.421
Your Highness!

39:15.521 --> 39:17.240
Something...

39:17.241 --> 39:18.381
What happened?

39:35.681 --> 39:36.821
Anping.

39:37.801 --> 39:38.941
Anping.

39:39.121 --> 39:40.861
What happened to Anping?

39:41.201 --> 39:44.021
Someone in Drunken Bordello

39:44.641 --> 39:45.781
beat him to death.

39:52.241 --> 39:54.181
Anping, don't scare me.

39:55.001 --> 39:56.461
Wake up.

39:56.561 --> 39:58.421
How could this happen?

39:59.161 --> 40:00.301
Anping.

40:26.281 --> 40:30.301
(Prudence and Caution)

40:41.401 --> 40:42.541
Ansu.

40:43.801 --> 40:44.941
You're awake.

40:50.161 --> 40:51.421
I'm sorry, Ansu.

40:52.351 --> 40:53.601
I couldn't reach there in time.

40:54.001 --> 40:55.141
The killer

40:55.601 --> 40:56.981
has been arrested.

41:09.481 --> 41:10.621
Who's there?

41:11.921 --> 41:13.200
- Song Han?
- Take him away.

41:13.201 --> 41:14.040
You...

41:14.041 --> 41:15.560
What are you doing?

41:15.561 --> 41:17.400
- Move it!
- Who are you to arrest me?

41:17.401 --> 41:18.880
Do you know who my father is?

41:18.881 --> 41:20.981
Song Han, how dare you arrest me?

41:22.521 --> 41:23.661
Anping...

41:25.761 --> 41:27.301
How did he

41:31.281 --> 41:33.021
get beaten to death?

41:36.221 --> 41:39.701
The incident happened
at Drunken Bordello.

41:40.761 --> 41:42.440
That Miao kid is a weakling.

41:42.441 --> 41:44.621
Yeah, and he's the Princess's brother?

41:44.701 --> 41:46.851
- Back then, Anping and Dongqi...
- Run along now.

41:47.361 --> 41:48.280
They were fighting

41:48.281 --> 41:49.501
over a courtesan.

41:50.241 --> 41:51.421
Stay there if you dare!

41:51.561 --> 41:52.781
Just you wait!

41:52.841 --> 41:54.701
I'll be waiting for you.

41:57.401 --> 41:58.360
Move it!

41:58.361 --> 41:59.501
Shoo!

42:00.961 --> 42:03.061
Soon after Anping walked out,

42:03.861 --> 42:05.341
he began to vomit blood

42:05.881 --> 42:07.101
and fainted.

42:07.641 --> 42:09.981
When my men and I found him
in an alleyway,

42:10.081 --> 42:11.221
he was already...

42:21.281 --> 42:23.301
How could this happen?

42:26.281 --> 42:28.381
He's my only brother.

42:43.961 --> 42:45.341
What about my parents?

42:47.321 --> 42:48.781
I've already talked

42:49.081 --> 42:50.381
to the elders in your family.

42:51.361 --> 42:53.541
Your father had a stroke,

42:54.281 --> 42:56.021
and the imperial physician
is with him now.

42:57.281 --> 42:58.541
Your mother

42:58.801 --> 43:01.861
fainted a few times from sadness.

43:02.761 --> 43:04.141
She's fine, though.

43:08.921 --> 43:10.061
Don't be afraid.

43:11.121 --> 43:12.261
Everything's fine.

43:13.681 --> 43:14.821
From now on,

43:16.321 --> 43:18.621
even if I'm the only one by your side,

43:20.441 --> 43:22.181
I will take good care of you.

43:38.631 --> 43:39.480
I think

43:39.481 --> 43:41.320
the Crown Prince admires you.

43:41.321 --> 43:43.080
You haven't met him many times,
have you?

43:43.081 --> 43:44.720
If you can become a good ruler,

43:44.721 --> 43:47.961
I will help you establish your power
and fight the evil forces.

43:48.481 --> 43:49.821
If you won't accept that,

43:50.271 --> 43:52.261
I don't mind having another enemy.

43:53.931 --> 43:58.410
♪I gaze at you, and all is calm♪

43:58.411 --> 44:02.171
♪The world is vast and turbulent♪

44:02.331 --> 44:06.721
♪Moving forward alone, the expectations
of many are hard to bear♪

44:06.901 --> 44:10.830
♪When the time comes,
I will cast aside a lifetime of pride♪

44:10.831 --> 44:13.810
♪To wear a flower stick for you♪

44:13.811 --> 44:16.020
♪Or perhaps my heart
yearns for the other side♪

44:16.021 --> 44:18.581
♪Yet there's no place for me
to go in the end♪

44:18.631 --> 44:22.201
♪Your presence by
my side is irreplaceable♪

44:22.261 --> 44:25.781
♪Like a ship crossing
the desolate river♪

44:25.791 --> 44:29.770
♪That brings me
through a chapter of my life♪

44:29.771 --> 44:33.801
♪You are the light
that saves me in the darkness♪

44:34.241 --> 44:37.701
♪Having you is a blessing♪

44:37.861 --> 44:40.041
♪My heart filled with warmth♪

44:40.061 --> 44:43.891
♪By your side,
I spend the rest of my life♪

44:44.221 --> 44:47.361
♪Your presence
by my side is irreplaceable♪

44:47.901 --> 44:51.311
♪Where my heart yearns
is where I will go♪

44:51.751 --> 44:55.291
♪Breaking waves over the desolate river♪

44:55.491 --> 44:59.160
♪The wind rises as my heart finds peace♪

44:59.161 --> 45:03.501
♪You are the light
that saves me in the darkness♪

45:03.561 --> 45:07.290
♪Having you is a blessing♪

45:07.291 --> 45:10.770
♪Only by being by your side♪

45:10.771 --> 45:15.451
♪I can spend the rest of my life♪

45:15.481 --> 45:19.070
♪Until the waves are all spread out♪

45:19.071 --> 45:23.211
♪And the past sinks into the river♪

45:23.281 --> 45:26.571
♪Always together, looking back♪

45:26.881 --> 45:34.181
♪Only sighing at the commotion♪

45:43.441 --> 45:44.400
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this drama.)

45:44.401 --> 45:45.400
(Every medical behaviour involved
and medicine used in the drama)

45:45.401 --> 45:46.661
(is required by the story.
Please don't try this at home.)
